<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/home.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/global.css" />
    <title>Professional Recipe Sharing Page</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- Include the header here -->
    <%- include("header.ejs") %>

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-background"></div>
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="title">
          <h1>
            Welcome to <span style="color: yellow">Recipe Sharing Page</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="sub-title">Your ultimate taste experience awaits!!!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-recipe">
      <fieldset style="border-radius: 10px">
        <legend><h2>About Recipe Oasis</h2></legend>
        <div class="about-details">
          <div class="about-description">
            <p>
              Welcome to Recipe Sharing, your go-to platform for discovering and
              sharing the best recipes from all over the world. Based in the
              vibrant city of London, we are passionate about bringing together
              food lovers from every corner of the globe.<br /><br />
              Our journey began in the heart of London, a city renowned for its
              diverse culinary scene. Inspired by the rich tapestry of flavors
              and cultures, Recipe Sharing was founded to celebrate this
              diversity and make it accessible to everyone. Whether you're a
              seasoned chef or a home cook, we invite you to join our community
              and share your culinary creations.<br /><br />
              At Recipe Sharing, we believe that food is a universal language
              that brings people together. Our platform allows you to explore
              new recipes, connect with fellow food enthusiasts, and showcase
              your own dishes. From traditional family recipes to modern twists
              on classic dishes, our community is a melting pot of culinary
              inspiration.
            </p>
            <br /><br />We are thrilled to welcome food lovers from all cities
            to our platform. No matter where you're from, your recipes and
            stories are valued here. Together, let's create a space where
            everyone can discover new tastes and share the joy of cooking.
            <p
              style="
                margin-top: 20px;
                font-size: 14px;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
              "
            >
              <span>Sincerely,</span>
              <i>- The Recipe Sharing Team</i>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-image">
            <img src="images/Picture_4.avif" alt="About Food Picture" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </fieldset>
    </section>

